No need for full repo checkout

Process transparently-compressed plain text attachments

See here: https://groups.google.com/g/zotero-dev/c/ZS7o5ymitFw/m/jo0lzFaUAQAJ
Move zipped plain file handling into retrieve method
Fix apparent Zotero API bug when retrieving plain-text attachments
Try to build and upload wheel as artifact
Try to ensure latest setuptools and pip
Richer error handling by preserving underlying error as __cause__ / __context__
